msgstr "Holding Distance (ໄລຍະຫ່າງທີ່ຢຶດໜ່ຽວໄວ້)&amp;nbsp;<br/>"

#. module: museum
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:museum.welcome_article_body
